sentences: Parties discussed how to move forward based on the LULUCF Annexes to previous AWG-KP reports (FCCC/KP/AWG/2008/3 and 5), and past and future party submissions.
Parties then discussed, inter alia , natural disturbances, non-permanence under the CDM and further activities under Protocol Article 3.4 (additional activities).
Further informal consultations will address submissions from the parties to clarify positions for next year.
